## purpose
Defines core runtime handling for culture.

## runtime_scope
Runtime covers cultural-context visibility,
pattern-aware display,
historical culture reference,
and safe failure rendering.

## validation_rules
- cultural context must resolve
- interpretation basis must resolve
- disclosure scope must be valid
- historical/reference mode must be valid

## failure_modes
- invalid cultural context
- invalid interpretation basis
- invalid historical mode
- safe runtime fallback

## observability
Runtime must emit enough signals
to distinguish active cultural context,
historical reference,
interpretation mode,
and failure surface.

## review_checklist
- cultural runtime scope is explicit
- interpretation-aware rendering is explicit
- failure handling is explicit
